source.name: Quality Database (QDB)
source.description: The Quality Database (QDB) System is a Web-based application. QDB serves as the data purity tool used to maintain data integrity and purity of Federal Logistics Information System (FLIS) data. QDB tracks requested changes to FLIS data to maximize data integrity and assist in discrepancies with the purpose of applying root-cause corrective action.  The Public Inquiry QDB user can search and view NIIN records and associated data only.
